snippet.title: SAND LAND — Game Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Dive into a desert world from the creator of Dragon Ball, Akira Toriyama! 
Play as the Fiend Prince, Beelzebub, and set off on an adventure using your wits, brawn, and vehicles to save #SANDLAND! 

Learn more: https://bnent.eu/Sand-Land

Follow Bandai Namco Entertainment: 
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/bandainamcous
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/BandaiNamcoUS
Twitter: https://twitter.com/BandaiNamcoUS
Twitch: http://www.twitch.tv/bandainamcous
